{"tid":2168361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★全民檢測｜政府招公務員協助最高時薪900元　選舉事務處負責佈場","createTime":"2020-08-21T16:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T06:55:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"309d1db869681ccb52e14c72826d02bef36d0e65","tid":2168361,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T16:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5108327/org/e1f6a0293c94d9694d52093ddbae8b30.jpg/JPAZU0XFWBlylpICqFwwr0di1m9ufwwS4c_81-HP_Nc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5108327%2Forg%2Fe1f6a0293c94d9694d52093ddbae8b30.jpg%2FJPAZU0XFWBlylpICqFwwr0di1m9ufwwS4c_81-HP_Nc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=554ed0da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n職位分四類 時薪最低$200<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局今日（21日）向內部部門發信，邀請部門主管提名在職公政府人員或退休公務員，在社區檢疫中心進行行政工作。據內部文件披露，職位分為四類，分別是中心主管（Centre Supervisor），<strong>時薪為900元</strong>，負責監督中心營運，包括人群控制、市民查詢等，第二類是中心主管助理（Assistant Centre Supervisor），<strong>時薪為540元</strong>，為中心主管提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n至於第三類職位是登記主任（Registration Officer），時薪為360元，負責協助市民進行網上登記，第四類是工作人員（Workman），時薪為200元，負責清潔、消毒、搬運、收貨等工作。工作日期為9月1日至9月14日，以輪更形式工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/513725/%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8B%9B%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%99%82%E8%96%AA900%E5%85%83-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BD%88%E5%A0%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F513725%2F%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%2596%25AA900%25E5%2585%2583-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%2599%2595%